Name: Snack Stall
About the game: About This game is a simulation fast food restaurant game. First of all, you have to play the role of the receptionist and firmly remember what the guests ordered. Only the correct dishes can bring income, and the wrong dishes must be compensated for the guests. Secondly, you have to fry eggs and steaks for the guests. Please remember the maturity of the omelettes and steaks that the guests want. The closer to the requirements of the guests, the higher the income. Third, you have to prepare drinks for the guests, according to the requirements of the guests, if it is wrong, it may lead to failure. Fourth, you have to make hamburgers for the guests. The guests will ask for a few pieces of meat, a few eggs, etc., and you need to record them immediately. Feature The difficulty of the game increases dramatically as the levels increase, making it ideal for those who are more than willing to challenge themselves.
